{"tid":984872,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（法律L入）想問我咁做會唔會太仆街？","createTime":"2019-01-17T06:44:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-18T03:21:31.000Z","uid":48456,"like":19,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"c7c7f5b31be505537b38c00770d84a4ba0b1d707","tid":984872,"uid":48456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:44:54.000Z","msg":"是咁的，屋企住村屋門口有塊空地，屋企人近日拎咗啲元貝返嚟生曬，咁我就去幫手反吓啦。咁橋隔離住咗一堆蝗，於是我反時用鍾景輝既語調大聲朗讀中史書入面49之後到文革嗰部份嘅內容，最後佢選擇開大收音機扮聽唔到。想問如果我keep 住日日都咁做會唔會出事？<br />\n<br />\nPS:隔離屋有兩個小蝗。"},{"pid":"787b3e926adf38d88bb16ec20cb42c15ca5a8bc7","tid":984872,"uid":107364,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf1e30969e8f34ff9ac9b2a5f731564a1457d30f","tid":984872,"uid":161341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢地錄到你片/音果啲就ok.<br />\n唔想煩就自己錄音日日播，當自己跳大媽舞is ok"},{"pid":"b66f60cebb0cd1ebcd60467de36771c574965bd8","tid":984872,"uid":226587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:22:50.000Z","msg":"0/10"},{"pid":"f7838106b46e1a4ce24cabd52e78eafe419eaead","tid":984872,"uid":48456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"787b3e926adf38d88bb16ec20cb42c15ca5a8bc7","tid":984872,"uid":107364,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T06:58:31.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:24:27.000Z","msg":"放緊sem break 冇搵part time"},{"pid":"59e7493d30f0406715bde4ddb2e13d9e724b281c","tid":984872,"uid":48456,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"cf1e30969e8f34ff9ac9b2a5f731564a1457d30f","tid":984872,"uid":161341,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T07:01:38.000Z","msg":"唔好比佢地錄到你片/音果啲就ok.<br />\n唔想煩就自己錄音日日播，當自己跳大媽舞is ok"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-17T08:24:46.000Z","msg":"巴打建議可以考慮"},{"pid":"1afaed32d052a9d27e765c6e9a71ab051e438814","tid":984872,"uid":48456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b66f60cebb0cd1ebcd